\id 2TH New Alpha - June 11, 2007
\h 2 TESALONICENSES
\toc3 2Ts
\toc2 2 Tesalonicenses
\toc1 RI UKABꞌ WUJ RI XUTZꞌIBꞌAJ RI PABLO CHIKE RI KOJONELABꞌ AꞌJ TESALÓNICA
\mt1 RI UKABꞌ WUJ RI XUTZꞌIBꞌAJ RI PABLO CHIKE RI KOJONELABꞌ AꞌJ TESALÓNICA
\imt2 Majibꞌal re
\ip Are xtzꞌibꞌataj ri nabꞌe wuj chike ri Tesalonicenses, ri Pablo xutzꞌibꞌaj chi jun wuj chike chusukꞌumaxik ri kikꞌutuꞌn ri esal taq kiwach ri e qꞌalajisal taj tzij rumal riꞌ xubꞌij chike chi ri uqꞌijal ri Dios kꞌulmatajinaq chik. Ri uqꞌijal ri Dios are jun tzij ri xkikoj ri e qꞌalajisal taq utzij ri Dios aꞌj Israel, jewaꞌ xkibꞌij rumal che ri xkiqꞌalajisaj ri uchꞌekenem ri Dios puꞌwiꞌ ri itzel xuqujeꞌ ri tojbꞌal ke ri e ralkꞌwaꞌl.
\ip Ri winaq aꞌj Tesalónica xkꞌaxir kikꞌuꞌx rumal chi pa kikꞌuꞌx chi xikꞌow ri upetibꞌal ri Cristo xuqujeꞌ chi aꞌreꞌ man xebꞌe ta rukꞌ, man ikꞌowinaq ta kꞌut. Rumal kꞌu che ri xkichapleꞌj uriqik kꞌax xaq are chi katzijox rij.
\ip Ri Pablo pune kꞌamajaꞌ kutzalij uwach ri kikꞌutuꞌn ri esal taq kiwach qꞌalajisal taq tzij, xubꞌij chike chi ri Dios kutoj na ri kꞌaxal ri xbꞌan chike ri kojonelabꞌ kumal ri man e kojonelabꞌ taj. Xuqujeꞌ ri Pablo kunaꞌtaj ronojel ri jastaq ri utzijom chike pa kiwinaqil xuqujeꞌ kunaꞌtaj chi ri upetibꞌal ri Ajawxel xnaqajir loq. Xuqujeꞌ kutzalij ubꞌixik chike ri ucholajil ri xubꞌij chike pa ri nabꞌe wuj jawjeꞌ kubꞌij wi chike chi choqꞌaqꞌ kechakunik kakichꞌek ri kakitijo, man xaq ta kesaqꞌorinik.
\ip Pa ri kꞌisbꞌal re ri wuj, ri xtzꞌibꞌax rumal jun ajtzꞌibꞌ, ri Pablo rukꞌ ri utzꞌibꞌ kutaq jun rutzil kiwach ri winaq aꞌj Tesalónica, rech jeriꞌ kakilo chi qas areꞌ xyoꞌw bꞌik ri kꞌutuꞌn.
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Ri Pablo, ri Silvano\f + \fr 1:1 \ft Are xuqujeꞌ Silas, are waꞌ ri achi ri xukꞌam bꞌik ri Pablo are xubꞌusolij ri kojonelabꞌ chukabꞌ mul. \xt Hechos 15:40.\xt*\f* xuqujeꞌ ri Timoteo chike ri e kojonelabꞌ ri e kꞌo pa ri komontyox ke ri aꞌj Tesalónica, chiꞌwe ix ri ix rech ri Dios xuqujeꞌ ri Tataxel rachiꞌl ri Ajawxel Jesucristo:
\v 2 Are ri Tataxel Dios xuqujeꞌ ri Ajawxel Jesucristo cheyoꞌw toqꞌobꞌ xuqujeꞌ jaꞌmaril chiꞌwe.
\s1 Tyoxinik che ri Dios xuqujeꞌ bꞌanoj chꞌawem
\p 
\v 3 Qachalal, sibꞌalaj choqꞌaqꞌ wi kujtyoxin che ri Dios rumal iwe, jetaq ri qas usukꞌ kabꞌanik, jeriꞌ rumal ri ikojobꞌal sibꞌalaj amaqꞌel tajin kakꞌiyik xuqujeꞌ tajin kanimar pa iwanimaꞌ ri loqꞌanik chike nikꞌaj chik.
\v 4 Rumal kꞌu riꞌ kaqanaꞌ nimal are kaqatzijoj iwij pa taq ri nikꞌaj ukomontyox ri Dios chik. Jeriꞌ rumal pune tajin kixikꞌow pa taq sibꞌalaj kꞌi kꞌax xuqujeꞌ jaljoj taq kꞌaxkꞌolal, xaq jeꞌ ko ix kꞌolik, jeqel ikꞌuꞌx chirij ri Dios.
\v 5 Ronojel waꞌ kukꞌutu chi sukꞌ ronojel ri uqꞌatoj tzij ri Dios, rumal kꞌu riꞌ ri Dios kubꞌan chiꞌwe chi taqalik kixkꞌojiꞌk pa ri rajawarem, ri rumal rech tajin kiriq kꞌax kamik.
\p 
\v 6 Ri Dios sibꞌalaj sukꞌ kuqꞌat na tzij pa kiwiꞌ ri kakibꞌan kꞌax chiꞌwe ix.
\v 7 Ri ix kꞌut ri kiriq kꞌax, kuya na uxlanem chiꞌwe, xuqujeꞌ kuya na uxlanem chaqe uj. We jastaq riꞌ kakꞌulmataj na are kukꞌut ribꞌ ri Ajawxel Jesús cho ri kaj, rukꞌ qꞌaqꞌ ri kajininik, e rachiꞌl ri rangelibꞌ ri kꞌo kikwinem,
\v 8 kuluqꞌata tzij pa kiwiꞌ ri man kakinimaj ta ri utz laj tzij rech ri Ajawxel Jesús.
\v 9 Ri winaq ri man kekojon ta che ri utz laj tzij kakiriq na jun alik kꞌaxkꞌolal, keꞌsax na bꞌik cho ri ukaꞌyebꞌal ri Ajawxel, kekꞌam na bꞌik naj jawjeꞌ ri man kekwin taj kakil wi ri ujuluwem xuqujeꞌ ri ukwinem ri Dios.
\v 10 Jeriꞌ kakꞌulmataj na pa ri qꞌij are kape ri Ajawxel Jesucristo rech jeriꞌ konojel ri utinimit ri uchaꞌom apanoq nim karilo xuqujeꞌ kuqꞌijilaꞌj. Ri ix kꞌut ix kachiꞌl we tinimit riꞌ rumal xixkojonik che ri qꞌalajisanik ri xqabꞌij chiꞌwe.
\p 
\v 11 Rumal riꞌ amaqꞌel kaqabꞌan chꞌawem pa iwiꞌ rech jeriꞌ ri Dios kubꞌano chi kataqiꞌk ri sikꞌinik ri xuya apanoq chiꞌwe xuqujeꞌ pa ri ukwinem chubꞌana pa iwanimaꞌ ronojel ri rayibꞌal ukꞌuꞌx rech utzilal xuqujeꞌ chutzꞌaqatisaj ronojel chak ri kabꞌan rukꞌ kojobꞌal.
\v 12 Rumal riꞌ kaqabꞌan chꞌawem pa iwiꞌ rech kaqꞌijilaꞌtaj na ri ubꞌiꞌ ri Ajawxel Jesús xa rumal iwe xuqujeꞌ kanimarisataj na iqꞌij ix rumal are, rumal ri utoqꞌobꞌ ri Dios xuqujeꞌ ri Ajawxel Jesucristo.
\c 2
\s1 Ri qꞌatoj tzij ri kape na puꞌwiꞌ ri itzel achi
\p 
\v 1 Qachalal, are kꞌu ri upetik ri Ajawxel Jesucristo xuqujeꞌ ri qariqoj ibꞌ rukꞌ areꞌ, qas kixqabꞌochiꞌj rech
\v 2 makꞌexen ri ichomabꞌal xuqujeꞌ makꞌaxir iwanimaꞌ rumal ri kabꞌix chiꞌwe chi xuriq ri upetibꞌal ri Ajawxel we kabꞌix chiꞌwe rumal jun uxlabꞌal, pa tzij ne kabꞌix chiꞌwe o xuqujeꞌ xane pa wuj tzꞌibꞌatal wi loq chiꞌwe pune qatzꞌibꞌ uj kabꞌantajik.
\v 3 Miya iwibꞌ pa subꞌik, ri uqꞌijal ri Ajawxel kꞌamajaꞌ kuriqo are nabꞌe kakꞌulmataj ri elik pa ri kojobꞌal xuqujeꞌ ri qꞌij are kukꞌut ribꞌ ri achi bꞌanal mak, ri ralkꞌwaꞌl etzelal.
\v 4 We achi riꞌ kubꞌan ukꞌulel che ronojel ri tzujtal cho ri Dios. Kubꞌan kꞌu na rech che ri Templo xuqujeꞌ kubꞌij na Dios chibꞌil ribꞌ.
\p 
\v 5 ¿La man kanaꞌtaj chiꞌwe chi xintzijoj waꞌ we riꞌ chiꞌwe are in kꞌo iwukꞌ?
\v 6 Iwetaꞌm chi kꞌo jun jastaq ri kaqꞌaten we achi riꞌ rech man kukꞌut ta na ribꞌ xane kꞌa te kukꞌut ribꞌ qas pa ri uqꞌijal.
\v 7 Je kꞌu riꞌ rumal cher tajin kachakun chik ri etzelal ri awatal loq, xaq xwi majaꞌ kesaxik ri tajin kaqꞌaten we achi riꞌ rech kukꞌut ribꞌ.
\v 8 We xikꞌow we riꞌ, kukꞌut na ribꞌ ri itzel achi, are riꞌ ri kakamisax na rumal ri Ajawxel rukꞌ ri Uxlabꞌal ri kel loq puꞌchiꞌ xuqujeꞌ katukix na rukꞌ ri utunal ri upetibꞌal ri Ajawxel.
\v 9 Are ri Itzel kabꞌanow na chi ri itzel achi kape na kulubꞌanaꞌ ronojel uwach mayijabꞌal taq jastaq, kꞌutbꞌal xuqujeꞌ jastaq ri xaq qꞌolobꞌal.
\v 10 Rukꞌ ronojel uwach etzelal kuꞌmenkꞌetij na konojel ri kasach kiwach, jeriꞌ rumal man xkaj taj xkiloqꞌaj ri qas tzij rumal riꞌ man xekolotaj taj.
\v 11 Rumal riꞌ, kuya na bꞌe ri Dios che we jastaq riꞌ kakꞌulmatajik rech rumal ri ukwinem ri subꞌunik, ri winaq kekojon na che ri bꞌanoj tzij.
\v 12 Rech jeriꞌ kaqꞌat na tzij pa kiwiꞌ konojel ri man xekojon ta che ri qas tzij, xane are xekiꞌkot chubꞌanik ri etzelal.
\s1 Taqchiꞌnik rech jeriꞌ kejeqiꞌ ri winaq pa ri kikojobꞌal
\p 
\v 13 Ri uj kꞌut rajawaxik kaqaya tyoxinik che ri Dios rumal iwe ix qachalal, rumal ix loqꞌ rumal ri Ajawxel, jeriꞌ rumal pa ri majibꞌal rech ronojel, ri Dios xixuchaꞌo rech kixkolotajik rumal ri chak rech ri Uxlabꞌixel ri katyoxirisanik xuqujeꞌ ri ikojobꞌal ri kꞌo pa ri qas tzij.
\v 14 Rumal waꞌ xixusikꞌij apanoq ri Dios rumal ri utz laj taq tzij ri xqatzijoj chiꞌwe, rech jeriꞌ kꞌo iwe che ri ujuluwem ri Ajawxel Jesucristo.
\p 
\v 15 Xaq jeriꞌ qachalal, kꞌo chixkꞌoloq xuqujeꞌ chixjeqeloq pa taq ri kꞌutuꞌn ri qabꞌim xuqujeꞌ qatzꞌibꞌam chiꞌwe.
\v 16 Tzaꞌre ri Ajawxel Jesucristo rachiꞌl ri Dios Tataxel ri xujuloqꞌaj xuqujeꞌ rumal ri utoqꞌobꞌ xukubꞌisaj qakꞌuꞌx chibꞌe qꞌij saq.
\v 17 Chixutaqchiꞌj xuqujeꞌ chuya uchuqꞌabꞌ ri iwanimaꞌ rech ta kꞌu pa tzij xuqujeꞌ pa ri chak are chibꞌana ri utzilal.
\c 3
\s1 Ri Pablo kuta chꞌawem rech kachikox ubꞌixik ri utz laj tzij
\p 
\v 1 Qachalal, kꞌisbꞌal re, chibꞌana chꞌawem pa qawiꞌ rech jeriꞌ aninaq kachikon ubꞌixik ri utzij ri Dios xuqujeꞌ nim kilik are kakꞌamawaꞌxik, jetaq ri xkꞌulmataj iwukꞌ ix.
\v 2 Chibꞌana xuqujeꞌ chꞌawem rech man kujqaj ta pa kiqꞌabꞌ itzel taq winaq, jeriꞌ rumal man konojel taj kꞌo kikojobꞌal pa Jesucristo.
\p 
\v 3 Ri Ajawxel kꞌut kubꞌan na ri kubꞌij, areꞌ kuya na ichuqꞌabꞌ xuqujeꞌ kixukol na cho ri Itzel.
\v 4 Kuꞌl qakꞌuꞌx chirij ri Ajawxel chi ri ix kibꞌano xuqujeꞌ kibꞌan na ri qakꞌutum chiꞌwach.
\v 5 Are bꞌa ri Dios chixutoꞌ rech jeriꞌ kixloqꞌanik xuqujeꞌ rech kajeqiꞌ ikꞌuꞌx jetaq ri xubꞌan ri Cristo xuchap ukꞌuꞌx churiqik ri kꞌaxal.
\s1 Choqꞌaqꞌ kabꞌan chakunem
\p 
\v 6 Qachalal, pa ri ubꞌiꞌ ri Ajawxel Jesucristo kixqataqchiꞌj rech kiqꞌat iwibꞌ che ri alaxik ri man je taj tajin kanoqꞌijik jetaq ri kubꞌij ri kꞌutuꞌn ri xqaya chiꞌwe.
\v 7 Ri ix iwetaꞌm jas rajawaxik kibꞌano rech je kixnoꞌjinik jetaq ri kujnoꞌjin uj. Man xujqꞌiꞌtaj taj are xujkꞌojiꞌ iwukꞌ.
\v 8 Xuqujeꞌ man xaq ta xqatij ri iwa xane xqatoj chiꞌwe. Xujchakunik rukꞌ chuqꞌabꞌ chi paqꞌij chi chaqꞌabꞌ rech jeriꞌ man xujux ta jun eqaꞌn chike jujun chiꞌwe.
\v 9 Jeriꞌ xqabꞌano, man xa ta rumal mat taqal chaqe kaqakꞌam ri tobꞌanik, xane are kaqaj kaqakꞌut chiꞌwach jas ri taqalik kixnoꞌjinik.
\v 10 Jeriꞌ rumal are xujkꞌojiꞌk iwukꞌ xqabꞌij chiꞌwe: Chi ri man karaj taj kachakunik, man waꞌ bꞌa.
\v 11 Xqetaꞌmaj chi e kꞌo jujun chiꞌxoꞌl ri xaq e saqꞌor, man kakaj taj kechakunik xuqujeꞌ kakinim kibꞌ pa taq kꞌulmatajik ke nikꞌaj chik.
\v 12 Keꞌqataqchiꞌj we winaq riꞌ xuqujeꞌ keꞌqayajo pa ri Ajawxel Jesucristo rech jeriꞌ kechakunik pa jororemal rech kakichꞌek ri kakitijo.
\p 
\v 13 Ri ix kꞌut qachalal, mixqꞌiꞌtajik chubꞌanik ri utzilal.
\v 14 We kꞌo jun man kunimaj ta we xqabꞌij chiꞌwe pa we wuj riꞌ, chitzujuj chikiwach konojel xuqujeꞌ makiwachiꞌlaj taj rech jeriꞌ kel ukꞌixibꞌal.
\v 15 Pune jeriꞌ kubꞌano, mibꞌan ikꞌulel che, xaq xwi chiyajaꞌ jetaq ri kibꞌano che jun iwachalal.
\s1 Kꞌisbꞌal rutzil wach
\p 
\v 16 Are ri Ajawxel rech jaꞌmaril chuya jaꞌmaril chiꞌwe pa ronojel ri kꞌaxkꞌolal. Are ri Ajawxel kakanaj kanoq iwukꞌ iwonojel.
\p 
\v 17 In in Pablo kintzꞌibꞌaj bꞌik we rutzil iwach riꞌ rukꞌ ri nuqꞌabꞌ xuqujeꞌ rukꞌ ri nutzꞌibꞌ. Are waꞌ retal ronojel ri nuwuj nukojom.
\v 18 Are ri utoqꞌobꞌ ri Ajawxel Jesucristo kakanaj iwukꞌ.
